DIGITAL SAVER - HEALTH MONITORING SYSTEM

This project includes a smartwatch health monitoring application developed
by Cambric under the Egyptian Government Digital Health Initiative.

Medical Disclaimer:
This software is provided for wellness and educational purposes only.
It is NOT a certified medical device and should NOT be used for:
- Medical diagnosis
- Clinical treatment decisions
- Replacement of professional medical advice
- Emergency medical response as the sole means

Always consult qualified healthcare professionals for any health concerns.
The developers of Digital Saver accept no liability for decisions made
based on the software's readings or recommendations.

For more information, visit:
https://github.com/asserkdev/Digital-saver/
